snippet.title: Bloodborne Kart Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Bloodborne Kart: RELEASING 1/31/2024! 

➡ 12 racers!
➡ 16 maps!
➡ Full single player campaign mode!
➡ Boss fights!
➡ Local split screen multiplayer!
➡ VS Battle mode!

Music by The Noble Demon: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rCBuxwBrHik
Cover art by Corwyn Prichard: https://twitter.com/art_mino
Announcer voiced by Gianni Matragrano: https://youtube.com/@GianniMatragrano?si=61cTgJGXmbpQPuMF
Press kit: http://fansoftware.org

Happy Halloween!
